More importantly, do you guys happen to know a Teenieping wearing glass slippers?

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:30.000
Glass slippers... Rellaping? She's the ultimate tomboy Princess Teenieping of the Bibidi Kingdom, poni.

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:31.000
Tomboy?

00:05:31.000 --> 00:05:33.000
Yeah.

