One day, Rellaping went to a ball held in the kingdom...

00:05:36.000 --> 00:05:44.000
She was having trouble getting in because her dress got dirty from playing in the dirt, but...

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:49.000
A fairy godmother appeared and made it possible for her to attend the ball, sappun.

00:05:49.000 --> 00:05:54.000
But that magic was only supposed to last until 12 o'clock...

00:05:54.000 --> 00:06:06.000
And Rellaping, who forgot about that, humiliated herself in front of everyone, poni.

